title: Should We Buy a Floor Priced NFT, or a Reasonably Priced Rare NFT?
body:
Reasoning: In our previous Google Form DAO vote, our community narrowed DAO Vault choices down to Mutant Ape Yacht Club, CyberKongz, and The Doge Pound. This vote will serve to conclude if we'll be adding a floor priced NFT, or a reasonably priced rare NFT to the DAO Vault. A Reasonably Priced Rare NFT would be purchased at the discretion of The Goobers team.

Mutant Ape Yacht Club: https://opensea.io/collection/mutant-ape-yacht-club
CyberKongz: https://opensea.io/collection/cyberkongz
The Doge Pound: https://opensea.io/collection/the-doge-pound

Timeline: We'll purchase an NFT from the winning collection after the conclusion of this vote.

Cost: The DAO will use DAO Wallet funds to purchase an NFT from the winning collection.
